name: Park Daugherty
about: Hi there! I'm Park Daugherty, a 35-year-old from Greenland. I work at BUZZWORKS, where I'm passionate about what I do and always strive to exceed expectations. In my free time, I love to spend time with my loved ones and take on new adventures. I'm excited to see what the future holds and what opportunities lie ahead.

name: Meagan Ashley
about: Meagan is currently employed at ASSISTIX, where she has quickly established herself as a valuable member of the team. Meagan's strong work ethic, attention to detail, and creative problem-solving skills have made her a sought-after colleague. Outside of work, Meagan enjoys exploring her city, trying new foods, and spending time with her friends and family. She is a well-rounded individual who is always looking for new opportunities to grow and learn.

name: Denise Garrison
about: I work at Vurbo, where I get to put my skills to the test every day and help drive the company's success. Outside of work, I love to immerse myself in the local culture and take in all that Nepal has to offer. I'm also an avid traveler and enjoy experiencing new sights, sounds, and tastes.
